description: Police are investigating the death of Onchan man Lee Peel, 50, whose body was found on Ramsey beach.
title: Man found dead on Isle of Man beach named by police as Lee Peel
title_page: Man found dead on Isle of Man beach named by police as Lee Peel - BBC News
maintext: A man who was found dead on a beach in the north of the Isle of Man has been named as Lee Peel.
